      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; FDA benchmark dataset provides a single pump specimen; sample variability is acknowledged but not quantified.",
      "rationale": "The FDA benchmark study used a single manufactured specimen of the generic centrifugal pump. Inter-specimen variability is not characterized in the validation dataset. This limitation is acknowledged; formal test sample assessment is not required at MRL 2."
    },
