    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40-2018 MRL 2 assessment table. Validation results demonstrate hemolysis index predictions within ±20% of experimental data across the full CPB operating envelope. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device as described in the Claim and Requirement documentation.",
